{
  "texts": [
    "In this study, they were recategorized as baby (0-2 years), children (2-17 years), adults (18-60) and old (60 +).",
    "Figure 10 presents the age distribution of the participants that took part in the studies.",
    "It is observed that half of the studies (N = 109, 50%) are carried out with adult participants.",
    "Few studies (N = 6, 3%) include children as participants.",
    "The participant age group is not specified in 47% of the studies (N = 101).Figure 11 indicates the gender distribution, and it is seen that more than half of them (N = 86, 40%) are carried out with both female and male participants."
  ]
}